        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This +2 resilient padded armor is woven from many strands of gut cord strung with dried organs and preserved xulgath scent glands. When worn, it infuses your body with a ghastly and nauseating flavor.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">F</span> envision</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You are grabbed or are hit by an unarmed attack</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> Your attacker must attempt a DC 28 Fortitude saving throw. Creatures with a stench aura, such as otyughs and xulgaths, are immune to this effect.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected and is immune to the effects of the noxious jerkin for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is sickened 1.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is sickened 1 and is slowed 1 for 1 round.</p>"
